sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Auth
    participant Controller
    participant DB

    User->>Frontend: Open My Orders
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/orders/myorders (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: getMyOrders
    Controller->>DB: Find orders by user
    DB-->>Controller: Orders
    Backend-->>Frontend: Orders JSON
    Frontend-->>User: Show list

    User->>Frontend: Open Admin Orders
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/orders (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token + admin
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: getOrders
    Controller->>DB: Find all orders
    DB-->>Controller: Orders
    Backend-->>Frontend: Orders JSON
    Frontend-->>User: Show admin list
